{"tid":1269327,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"頭先係政總比撐警女人搶電話，但我同幾位人證都比一批警察圍、大聲斥喝，警察唔太想落案","createTime":"2019-06-30T14:02:17.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-01T23:48:04.000Z","uid":269421,"like":107,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":28,"replies":[{"pid":"f8f1a6f52a450ef075f707f1d6f1d87f374561b4","tid":1269327,"uid":269421,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-30T14:02:17.000Z","msg":"當時我拍緊嘅片：<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/story.php?story_fbid=2373281672925731&amp;id=1546925482228025\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fstory.php%3Fstory_fbid%3D2373281672925731%26id%3D1546925482228025&d=O1gn%2BLisHAK1lZrgQK9vXAz7jHi%2Fw8vyA5J9XtqU0Cw%3D&h=4f826736\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/story.php?story_fbid=2373281672925731&amp;id=1546925482228025</a><br />\n事發期間：<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/hkindigenous/posts/2373223859598179\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fhkindigenous%2Fposts%2F2373223859598179&d=O1gn%2BLisHAK1lZrgQK9vXAz7jHi%2Fw8vyA5J9XtqU0Cw%3D&h=7cfec7bb\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/hkindigenous/posts/2373223859598179</a><br />\n<br />\n希望收集現場片段，重現整個過程，呼籲現場有拍片既人send佢有既片比我：可以email：hhk77703@gmail.com，又或者upload上網比我。<br />\n<br />\n事發經過：<br />\n1. 係政總見到有義士比撐警集會支持者鬧，我舉起電話開始拍片。<br />\n2. 該名身穿藍色衫既女人走近鏡頭，口入面一路吟「影啦⋯⋯人在做⋯⋯天在看」忽然個女人申手搶電話，在場其他人眼見女人郁手，上前起哄。<br />\n3. 現場有大量警察，其中一群（大約十數人）前行過黎隔開個女人同我，我向警察提出要報案。 現場有幾位人證，表示見到女人搶電話。<br />\n4. 警察（包括一位不願透露編號既梁總督察）開始大聲斥喝本人（受害者、報案者）以及其他人證。<br />\n5. 「係咪要報警呀！」（態度極度惡劣）梁總督察大聲斥喝⋯⋯「要報警呀嘛，跟我返差館」<br />\n6. 其他人證事後都表示警察「幾個人圍佢地」、「好大聲，想嚇走佢地」「想大走佢地」<br />\n7. 五六個警察圍左我大半個鐘，期間當我係罪犯，多過受害人。其中梁總督察當我犯咁看待。態度差不特止，仲唔太願意提供幫助。另外，有一位人證話警察引導佢講「個女人拉我電話」而唔係「搶我電話」。<br />\n8. 最終，由於我不願意跟佢「返差館」，而現場又開始多黑衫民眾圍觀支持，佢要求我之後自己上中環警署落口供。"},{"pid":"4241554b9d01d690206b6e1449488662604316eb","tid":1269327,"uid":63117,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-30T14:03:50.000Z","msg":"極醜惡<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6be0ad087fa2dfa3274e6d812e337519ce9b875f","tid":1269327,"uid":94834,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-30T14:04:29.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"9c77466f29654b1eb313003ab3415fe8ae535f12","tid":1269327,"uid":200687,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-30T14:06:05.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f4242737be6120840466703897b8b4d6e8908a4a","tid":1269327,"uid":50275,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-30T14:06:23.000Z","msg":"屌，見到啲狗惡到呢，撐警團犯法唔使拉"},{"pid":"0ae684f7c528be31616bbcaecb8faf54f92f25db","tid":1269327,"uid":62749,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-30T14:06:33.000Z","msg":"唉, 唔好再信班狗會保護人"},{"pid":"f4a79fb4014a2da891fa45462e91f58c11a1a715","tid":1269327,"uid":213781,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-30T14:08:43.000Z","msg":"選擇性執法"},{"pid":"a8460eaa55af84d1cae0bacd31eb81ffac277cdb","tid":1269327,"uid":213781,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-30T14:08:56.000Z","msg":"做人做狗自己揀"},{"pid":"06f5a5add9c092b58ec979124207932e397c5c0c","tid":1269327,"uid":52939,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-30T14:13:28.000Z","msg":"如果反送中果班有咁惡<br />\n一早就衝左入政總吊起林鄭同鄭若打"},{"pid":"54dd5005e286ea2d4bb36d3c37aa2f91d57de508","tid":1269327,"uid":260740,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-30T14:16:35.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"59ab79ebe57f1ca45c5e253ffad7d14a9295e3e5","tid":1269327,"uid":55130,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-30T14:26:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dea022858914255cddad63c9e5e17b65c5c6299b","tid":1269327,"uid":215876,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-30T14:29:19.000Z","msg":"當警隊不再中立時<br />\n又唔肯清除瘀血<br />\n是否可以解散<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"